mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
Pokemon Red spawn rates before first gym:
- The user starts the game in Pallet town
- After choosing his starter pokemon he advances towards the next town
- On the way there he may encounter several pokemon in the wild
- Each pokemon has a spawn rate depending on the area
- Upon reaching Pewter City the player can challenge the first gym
